CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 25, 1950, pg. 20 reads: "Knows His Stuff - William Anderson, who is currently leading the Steel City Bowling League, is considered to be one of the most improved bowlers in city. Mr. Anderson, who also captains The Courier Bowling Team, is averaging 160 against some pretty tough competition. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William Anderson wearing cuffed pants and medallion pattern tie, bowling in alley
